b'#!/bin/bash\n\n# Bail out if anything goes wrong\nset -e\n\n# Make sure Homebrew and DocBook are present\nwhich -s brew\ndocbook="$(brew --prefix docbook)"\ntest -d "$docbook"\n\n# Make sure the XML catalog is present\ntest -d /etc/xml || mkdir /etc/xml\ntest -f /etc/xml/catalog || xmlcatalog --noout --create /etc/xml/catalog\n\n# Register DocBook in the global XML catalog\nfor catalog in "$docbook"/docbook/{xml,xsl}/*/catalog.xml; do\n\txmlcatalog --noout --del "file://$catalog" /etc/xml/catalog\n\txmlcatalog --noout --add "nextCatalog" "" "file://$catalog" /etc/xml/catalog\ndone'

b'#include <iostream>\r\nusing namespace std;\r\n\r\nint main()\r\n{\r\n    int n;\r\n    cin >> n;\r\n    long long v[n];\r\n    for(int i=1;i<=n;i++)\r\n        cin >> v[i];\r\n    bool ok=0;\r\n    int x;\r\n    for(int i=2;i<=n;i++)\r\n    {\r\n        x=v[i]%2;\r\n        if(v[i-1]%2==x && v[i+1]%2==x)\r\n        {\r\n            ok=1; i=n;\r\n            cout << "DA";\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    if(ok==0)\r\n        cout << "NU";\r\n    return 0;\r\n}'

Acidic moonrays carve through each of those alike, rendering blades and sword arms worthless in his wake.\r\n\r\nAn icy chill grips those under his gaze, warning them of the true nature of death -\r\n\r\n"It comes for us all."\r\n\r\nHe\'s not the type for many words, but the grasp of oblivion itself tells a story that ends legacies, dynasties, empires -\r\n\r\none death at a time, sadly. One death at a time.\r\n\r\n"You will feel nothing on the other side."\r\n\r\nHis promise to the slain.\r\n(Peacekeeper)\r\n\r\n[16:48] Awa ran with his group to take something down of Crafthold, he hopes he does his best! It would be an exciting fight if it were not for his people, it if were not for Ardent.\r\n\r\nHe grabs his sword, pointing to his enemy. The battlelines fall and two warriors meet eye to eye -\r\n\r\none shrouded in robes and an aura of corrosive decay, with eyes like silver moons with swirls of cyan energies swimming through his eyes. His blade is alight in a cloak of sapphire-colored mana, blazing around the single-edged sword atop the knightly hilt.\r\n\r\nA medallion recognizable, perhaps, to some Fourfold members hangs around his neck - it\'s the Medal of Bravery awarded to Nakano Yeong so long ago. A gift to a hero of Jianghu.\r\n\r\nHis voice sends a shiver down the Ookami\'s spine. Hollow. Cold. Emotionless.\r\n\r\n"I wish no harm upon you, stranger. Please do not make me hurt you for the people of Crafthold.\r\n\r\nThis is my home."\r\n\r\nDespite that plea, his sword remains in a defensive stance, and the energies still flare. At the slightest hint of aggressive movement,he attacks with blinding speed.\r\n(Peacekeeper)\r\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n[16:56] ** Aw\xc3\xa1 has inflicted an injury upon Peacekeeper. ("Permanent Injury", "Permanent Injury", "Permanent", "Severity: MODERATE (-20 Vit)") **\r\n[17:07] Awa never fought against an undead, it scared him a little before the start of the fight, but he could not fear anyone, he will need to win, no matter what happens.\r\n\r\nAt the first moment, Peacekeeper easily reached Awa so many times, his sword was way sharper than Awa\'s sword, dealing an overwhelming damage towards Awa\'s body.\r\n\r\nHowever, Awa is tough, his Mythril armor was helping him A LOT! After being attacked several times by Peacekeeper, he was already almost falling to the ground, the moment that Peacekeeper started to run around him with clones- Awa panicked.\r\n\r\nHe stopped with his defense for a while to think about the possibility to run! Not a wise decision, he was knocked down by Peacekeeper.\r\n\r\nAshamed, Awa got up. He can\'t let a crime against Kraus\'s will alive, not now. He got up, ready to fight, not caring about the fate that will befall him if he fails.\r\n\r\n"Short lives are blessing." With that said, they proceeded with the fight, Awa was way tougher than before- his claw prepared to be used, he was quite prideful about his race, and the claw only helps.\r\n\r\nWith a powerful attack made by his claw and helped by his wild spirit, Peacekeeper was almost destroyed, he tried to run... Not enough. However, he is tough as Awa, he would not run nor lose that time. \r\n\r\nWhen Awa finally learned to fight against him, it was sorta easier, but still hard! Awa had no time to wait for him, he decided to attack him as soon as possible, and it was what happened, Awa quickly attacked Peacekeeper and weakened him.\r\n\r\nHowever, he had the chance to win yet, he had the chance and kinda tried to take advantage of that change, his attempt to hit and run Awa was almost being successful, but... It did not happen. Awa reached him and hit a powerful blow right on his undead body.\r\n\r\nHowever, he did not manage to kill that aberration now, unfortunately, but he spent the time he had to carve his body, he stepped on his belly with his right foot, and with Hestia\'s sword, he carved the word "KRAUS". Although it was not enough, he channeled energy through his sword to send his energy magic to the injury, causing its permanence.\r\n\r\nWhen he tried to destroy the head of that aberration with his sword, the horrific creature ran.\r\n\r\nLucky.\r\n(Aw\xc3\xa1)\r\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n[17:27] Peacekeeper does not fight as others do, and that might set Awa a little off-guard. Peacekeeper jumps from place to place on the battlefield covered in a shroud of blazing moonlight mixed with corrosive gases. His advance begins as him gliding along the ground before quickly changing direction, aiming to disorient the opponent and draw lines of toxic light across the battlefield.\r\n\r\nWhen his sword connects with the Ookami\'s body, the lunar runes adorning his body blaze with blue energies, seeming like they\'re going to burst -\r\n\r\nand on the impact, there\'s an explosion of cyan light, sending undead and Ookami alike tumbling across the battlefield. Peacekeeper falls limp in preparation for the tumble, before catching the ground with his sword and near-instantly slamming his feet into the ground.\r\n\r\n"I am not as human as you are, Ookami. But I will be, and you cannot stop that."\r\n\r\nThe inscriptions on either side of the sword blaze with silver light, cutting lines throughout the shroud of blue.\r\n\r\nHe charges for another advance, more aggressive than the last -\r\n\r\nshrouded in a cloak of moonlight that sprays a biting cold along Awa\'s wounds, the undead knight presses past his attacks, trading too much damage for too little reward. The claw pierces through his armor, scrapes one of his ribs, and provokes another explosion of mana - this time only sending Peacekeeper flying, and this time the runes grow dimmer.\r\n\r\nExhaustion. It\'s obvious, as he rolls to his feet once more, with all the clacks and clanks of hollow bones slamming against armor.\r\n\r\n"My life is not yours to end. My life is mine to take. I do not desire a peaceful rest."\r\n\r\nAs Peacekeeper speaks, then, the cyan light fades to a sickening green and moonlight seems to deplete - taking on the scent and sight of only the most powerful of acids. His voice takes on passion, anger, hate. Chilling to the core.\r\n\r\n"You will not end me."\r\n\r\nAgain, Peacekeeper advances, far too aggressive to care for his safety. Awa\'s attacks fly straight through his guard and the undead knight, rather than blasting away again, crumples into a pile of bones, faintly glowing with silver light. His sword is placed safely in its sheath, unable to be touched by fallen, limp hands.\r\n\r\nWeak.\r\n\r\nVulnerable.\r\n\r\nAn easy kill.\r\n\r\nAs Awa leaps to deliver the name \'Kraus,\' the silver light only grows in intensity. Colder... colder... the air grows peaceful and silent.\r\n\r\nAs the energy is burned into the undead\'s chest, he seems completely unconscious - his eyes are completely dim, and the only movement on hisbody is the gathering of silver light inside his armor.\r\n\r\nAs Awa raises his weapon for the deathstroke -\r\n\r\n"Not today."\r\n\r\npop-PCHOO!\r\n\r\nA massive explosion caused by the bursting of a bubble of hidden moon mana leaves a crater in the battlefield underneath them, sending them flying in completely different directions.\r\n\r\nPeacekeeper hits the ground running, with his sword in his sheath.\r\n(Peacekeeper)'

b'from picamera.array import PiRGBArray\r\nfrom picamera import PiCamera\r\nfrom PIL import Image\r\nimport numpy as np\r\nimport time\r\nimport cv2\r\nimport sys\r\n\r\nWIDTH = 640\r\nHEIGHT = 480\r\nFRAME_RATE = 10\r\n\r\n\r\ndef setup_camera():\r\n    camera = PiCamera()\r\n    camera.resolution = (WIDTH, HEIGHT)\r\n    camera.framerate = FRAME_RATE\r\n    rawCapture = PiRGBArray(camera, size=(WIDTH, HEIGHT))\r\n    time.sleep(0.1)\r\n    return camera, rawCapture\r\n\r\n\r\ndef get_mask_by_color(image):\r\n    hsv = cv2.cvtColor(image, cv2.COLOR_BGR2HSV)\r\n    low_blue = np.array([155,50,50])\r\n    up_blue = np.array([180,255,255])\r\n    return hsv, low_blue, up_blue\r\n\r\n\r\ndef apply_threshold_to_mask(image, hsv, low_blue, up_blue):\r\n    kernel = np.ones((10,10), np.uint8)\r\n    erosion = cv2.erode(image, kernel, iterations=1)\r\n    mask = cv2.inRange(hsv, low_blue, up_blue)\r\n    res = cv2.bitwise_and(image, image, mask=mask)\r\n    opening = cv2.morphologyEx(mask, cv2.MORPH_OPEN, kernel)\r\n    return mask, opening\r\n\r\n\r\ndef get_object_location(opening):\r\n    left = 0\r\n    right = 0\r\n    center = 0\r\n    for x in range(WIDTH):\r\n        for y in range(HEIGHT):\r\n            pixel = opening.getpixel((x,y))\r\n            color = getRed(pixel)\r\n            if color != 255:\r\n                continue\r\n            if x < 213:\r\n                left += 1\r\n            elif x < 426:\r\n                center += 1\r\n            else:\r\n                right += 1\r\n    if center == max([left, right, center]):\r\n        return \'center\'\r\n    if left == max([left, right, center]):\r\n        return \'left\'\r\n    if right == max([left, right, center]):\r\n        return \'right\'\r\n\r\n\r\ndef main():\r\n    camera, rawCapture = setup_camera()\r\n    for frame in camera.capture_continuous(rawCapture, format="bgr",\r\n                                          use_video_port=True):\r\n        \r\n        image = frame.array\r\n        hsv = cv2.cvtColor(image, cv2.COLOR_BGR2HSV)\r\n        low_blue = np.array([155,50,50])\r\n        up_blue = np.array([180,255,255])\r\n        kernel = np.ones((10,10), np.uint8)\r\n        erosion = cv2.erode(image, kernel, iterations=1)\r\n        mask = cv2.inRange(hsv, low_blue, up_blue)\r\n        res = cv2.bitwise_and(image, image, mask=mask)\r\n        opening = cv2.morphologyEx(mask, cv2.MORPH_OPEN, kernel)\r\n        # location = get_object_location(opening)\r\n        cv2.imshow("Mask", image)\r\n        cv2.waitKey(0) & 0xFF\r\n        # cv2.imshow("Image", opening)\r\n        rawCapture.truncate(0)\r\n        time.sleep(0.5)\r\n\r\n\r\nif __name__ == "__main__":\r\n    main()'

b'function sendForm()\n    {\n        $("#divSucesso").hide();\n        $("#divError").hide();\n\n        document.getElementById("btnEnviarForm").disabled = true;\n        var formAgenda = document.getElementById("form");\n        var formData = new FormData (formAgenda);\n\n        $.ajax({\n            url: \'insert.php\',\n            method: "POST",\n            data: formData,\n\n            cache: false,\n            processData: false,\n            contentType: false,\n\n            success: function (result) {\n\n                if (result.substring(0, 2) == "OK")\n                {\n                    document.getElementById(\'divSucesso\').innerHTML = "Dados salvos com sucesso: " + result;\n                    $("#divSucesso").stop().fadeIn(200).delay(2500).fadeOut(200);\n                    document.getElementById("btnEnivarForm").disabled = false;\n                    document.getElementById("form").reset();\n                }\n                else\n                  showMessageError(result);\n            },\n\n            error: function (xhr, status, error) {   \n                var errorMsg = xhr.responseText;\n                document.getElementById("errorMsg").innerHTML = errorMsg;\n                $("divError").fadeIn(200);\n                document.getElementById("btnEnviarForm").disabled = false;\n            }\n        });\n    }\n\n    function showMessageError(message)\n    {\n        document.getElementById("errorMsg").innerHTML = message;\n        $("#divError").fadeIn(200);\n    }\n</script>'

b"% Calculates and displays Magnitude, Phase and Groupdelay\r\n% of a third-order low-pass filter \r\n% \r\n% \r\n% syntax : [mg,ph,gd]=lp3(R1,R1t,R2,R2t,R3,R3t,R4,R4t,R5,R5t,R6,R6t,R7,R7t,C1,C1t,C2,C2t,C3,C3t,w);\r\n%\r\n% input:  \r\n%  \tR1-R7 ... Resistors\r\n%\tR1t-R7t..Tolerance\t\r\n%  \tC1-C3 ... Capacitors\r\n%\tC1t-C3t..Tolerance\t\r\n%\tw ..........Angular frequency in Rad/s\r\n%\t\r\n% Testsettings:\r\n%\tw=linspace(0,9000,901);\r\n% lp3(820,5,820,5,10000,5,1500,5,1200,5,1,0,1,0,22*10^-9,20,47*10^-9,20,22*10^-9,20,w);\r\n%\r\n%\r\n% Stingler Roman // 2012\r\n\r\nfunction [mg,ph,gd]=lp3(R1,R1t,R2,R2t,R3,R3t,R4,R4t,R5,R5t,R6,R6t,R7,R7t,C1,C1t,C2,C2t,C3,C3t,w);\r\n\t\t\r\na1=0.7560;\r\na2=0.9996;\r\nb1=0.4772;\r\n\r\nf0=4500;\r\nwc=2*pi*f0;\r\ns=((2*pi*w')/wc)*1i;\r\n\r\nHs1=(1+R3/R4)./(1+wc*R5*C3*s);\r\nHs2=1./(1+wc*C1*(R1+R2)*s+wc^2*R1*R2*C1*C2*s.^2);\r\nHs=Hs1.*Hs2;\r\n\r\nfor i=2:length(w)\r\nGd=(arg(Hs(i))-arg(Hs(i-1)))/(w(i)-w(i-1));\r\nend\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n%output Groupdelay\r\nfigure;\r\nplot(w,Gd);\r\n%plot(w,abs(Hsh));\r\n%errorbar (w, abs(Hs1));\r\ngrid on;\r\ntitle('Groupdelay');\r\n%xlabel('Frequency w in rad/s');\r\n%ylabel('Magnitude');\r\nhold on;\r\n\r\n%output Phase\r\nfigure;\r\n%errorbar (w, arg(Hs1));\r\nplot(w,arg(Hs));hold on;\r\n%plot(w,arg(Hsh));\r\ngrid on;\r\ntitle('Phase');\r\nxlabel('Frequency w in rad/s');\r\nylabel('Phase in degrees');\r\nhold on;\r\n\r\n%output Magnitude\r\nfigure;\r\nplot(w,abs(Hs));hold on;\r\n%plot(w,abs(Hsh));\r\n%errorbar (w, abs(Hs1));\r\ngrid on;\r\ntitle('Magnitude');\r\nxlabel('Frequency w in rad/s');\r\nylabel('Magnitude');\r\nhold on;"

    {\n            TaskCompletionSource<string> tcs = new TaskCompletionSource<string>();\n\n            Camera.TakePicture(UIApplication.SharedApplication.KeyWindow.RootViewController,\n                               (imagePickerResult) => \n            {\n                if(imagePickerResult == null)\n                {\n                    tcs.TrySetResult(null);\n                    return;\n                }\n\n                var photo = imagePickerResult.ValueForKey(new\n                                                          NSString("UIImagePickerControllerOriginalImage")) as UIImage;\n\n                var documentDirectory = Environment.GetFolderPath(Environment.SpecialFolder.Personal);\n                string jpgFileName = Path.Combine(documentDirectory, string.Format("fugitivo_{0}.jpg", Guid.NewGuid()));\n\n                NSData imgData = photo.AsJPEG();\n                NSError err = null;\n\n                if(imgData.Save(jpgFileName, false, out err))\n                {\n                    string result = "";\n                    result = jpgFileName;\n                    tcs.TrySetResult(result);\n                }\n                else\n                {\n                    tcs.TrySetException(new Exception(err.LocalizedDescription));\n                }\n            });\n\n            return tcs.Task;\n        }\n    }\n\n\tpublic null)\n\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t\t}\n\n\t\t\tpicker = new UIImagePickerController();\n\t\t\tpicker.Delegate = new CameraDelegate();\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tpublic static void TakePicture(UIViewController parent, Action<NSDictionary> callback)\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tCameraInit();\n\t\t\tpicker.SourceType = UIImagePickerControllerSourceType.Camera;\n\t\t\t_callback = callback;\n\t\t\tparent.PresentViewController((UIViewController)picker, true, (Action)null);\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tclass CameraDelegate : UIImagePickerControllerDelegate\n\t\t{\n\t\t\tpublic override void FinishedPickingMedia(UIImagePickerController picker, NSDictionary info)\n\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\tvar cb = _callback;\n\t\t\t\t_callback = null;\n\n\t\t\t\tpicker.DismissViewController(true, (Action)null);\n\t\t\t\tcb(info);\n\t\t\t}\n\n\t\t\tpublic override void Canceled(UIImagePickerController picker)\n\t\t\t{\n\t\t\t\tvar cb = _callback;\n\t\t\t\t_callback = null;\n\n\t\t\t\tpicker.DismissViewController(true, (Action)null);\n\t\t\t\tcb(null);\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t}\n}'

b'function search(Phrase, FolderID) {\n  // Prompt the user for a search term\n  var searchTerm = Browser.inputBox("Enter the string to search for:");\n\n  // Get the active spreadsheet and the active sheet\n  var ss = SpreadsheetApp.getActiveSpreadsheet();\n  var sheet = ss.getActiveSheet();\n\n  // Set up the spreadsheet to display the results\n  var headers = [["File Name", "File Type", "URL"]];\n  sheet.clear();\n  sheet.getRange("A1:C1").setValues(headers);\n\n  // Search the files in the user\'s Google Drive for the search term based on if the word is included in thefile or name\n  // Search Reference Guide: https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/drive/drive-app#searchFiles(String)\n  var files = DriveApp.searchFiles("fullText contains \'"+searchTerm.replace("\'","\'")+"\'");\n  //var SearchString = \'fullText contains "\' + Phrase + \'" and "\' + FolderID + \'" in parents\';\n  //var files = DriveApp.searchFiles(SearchString);\n  // create an array to store our data to be written to the sheet \n  var output = [];\n  // Loop through the results and get the file name, file type, and URL\n  while (files.hasNext()) {\n    var file = files.next();\n\n    var name = file.getName();\n    var type = file.getMimeType();\n    var url = file.getUrl();\n    // push the file details to our output array (essentially pushing a row of data)\n    output.push([name, type, url]);\n  }\n  // write data to the sheet\n  sheet.getRange(2, 1, output.length, 3).setValues(output);\n}\r\n\t\r\nfunction search(Phrase, FolderID) {\n  // Prompt // create an array to store our data to be written to the sheet \n  var output = [];\n  // Loop through the results and get the file name, file type, and URL\n  while (files.hasNext()) {\n    var file = files.next();\n\n    var name = file.getName();\n    var type = file.getMimeType();\n    var url = file.getUrl();\n    var folderNames = "";\n    var folders = file.getParents();\n    while (folders.hasNext()) {\n        var folder = folders.next();\n        folderNames += folder.getName() == ", ";\n    }\n    // push the file details to our output array (essentially pushing a row of data)\n    output.push([name, type, url, folders]);\n  }\n  // write data to the sheet\n  sheet.getRange(2, 1, output.length, 4).setValues(output);\n}\r\n\t\r\nwhile (files.hasNext()) {\n    var file IsWalking());\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbreak;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n\t\t\t\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t}\r\n\t\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t}\r\n\r\n\tif (IsWalking() || m_GraphicThingInstance.IsUsingMovingSkill())\r\n\t{\r\n\t\tfloat fRotation = m_GraphicThingInstance.GetRotation();\r\n\t\tfloat fAdvancingRotation = m_GraphicThingInstance.GetAdvancingRotation();\r\n\t\tint iDirection = GetRotatingDirection(fRotation, fAdvancingRotation);\r\n\r\n\t\tif (DEGREE_DIRECTION_SAME != m_iRotatingDirection)\r\n\t\t{\r\n\t\t\tif (DEGREE_DIRECTION_LEFT == iDirection)\r\n\t\t\t{\r\n\t\t\t\tfRotation = fmodf(fRotation + m_fRotSpd*m_GraphicThingInstance.GetSecondElapsed(), 360.0f);\r\n\t\t\t}\r\n\t\t\telse if (DEGREE_DIRECTION_RIGHT == iDirection)\r\n\t\t\t{\r\n\t\t\t\tfRotation = fmodf(fRotation - m_fRotSpd*m_GraphicThingInstance.GetSecondElapsed() + 360.0f, 360.0f);\r\n\t\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t\tif (m_iRotatingDirection != GetRotatingDirection(fRotation, fAdvancingRotation))\r\n\t\t\t{\r\n\t\t\t\tm_iRotatingDirection = DEGREE_DIRECTION_SAME;\r\n\t\t\t\tfRotation = fAdvancingRotation;\r\n\t\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\t\tm_GraphicThingInstance.SetRotation(fRotation);\r\n\t\t}\r\n\r\n\t\tif (__IsInDustRange())\r\n\t\t{\r\n\t\t\tfloat fDustDistance = NEW_GetDistanceFromDestPixelPosition(m_kPPosDust);\r\n\t\t\tif (IsMountingHorse())\r\n\t\t\t{\r\n\t\t\t\tif (fDustDistance > CInstanceBase::__ProcessFunctionEmotion(DWORD dwMotionNumber, DWORD dwTargetVID, const TPixelPosition & c_rkPosDst)\r\n{\r\n\tif (IsWalking())\r\n\t\tEndWalkingWithoutBlending();\r\n\r\n\t__EnableChangingTCPState();\r\n\tSCRIPT_SetPixelPosition(c_rkPosDst.x, c_rkPosDst.y);\r\n\r\n\tCInstanceBase * pTargetInstance = b"//Functional Class\n//Convert the following code into a functional class that produces a dog object\n\n//original 'dog' obj\nconst dog = {\n  name: 'Scout',\n  breed: ['Husky', 'German Shepherd'],\n  age: 4,\n  happiness: 50,\n  hunger: 10,\n  energy: 100,\n  play: function(){\n\n  },\n  feed: function() {\n\n  }\n};\n\n// Functional Class to Create Dog Obj\nconst dogCreator = function(name, breed, age) {\n  let dog = {};\n  dog.name = name;\n  dog.breed = breed;\n  dog.age = age;\n\n  dog.feed = function() {\n    if (dog.hunger - food > 0) {\n      dog.hunger -= food;\n    } else {\n      dog.hunger = 0;\n    }\n  },\n  dog.play = function() {\n    if (dog.happiness + time < 100) {\n      dog.happiness += time;\n    } else {\n      dog.happiness = 100;\n    }\n  \n    if (dog.energy - time > 0) {\n      dog.energy -= time;\n    } else {\n      dog.energy = 0;\n    }\n  }\n\n  return dog;\n}"

b'// Alex Brown CS161 Lab 8\n#include <iostream>\n#include <string>\n#include <set>\n\nusing namespace std;\n\nbool isIsogram(const char word[], const int len) {\n\tset<char> set;\n\tfor (int i = 0; i < len; i++) {\n\t\tif (!set.insert(word[i]).second) // no duplicates in sets\n\t\t\treturn false;\t\n\t}\n  \n\treturn true;\n}\n\nint main() {\n\tstring input;\n\t\n\tcout << "Enter your word: ";\n\tgetline(cin, input);\n\n\tif (isIsogram(input.c_str(), input.length())) // Pass in the string as a char arr and get a length, since it will change as a pointer\n\t\t\tcout << "Your word is an isogram" << endl;\n\telse\n\t\t\tcout << "Your word isn\'t an isogram" << endl;\n\n\treturn 0;\n}'

b'#include <stdlib.h>\r\n#include <iostream>\r\n#include <fstream>\r\n#include <stdlib.h>\r\n#include <string.h>\r\nusing namespace std;\r\n\r\nstruct NODO\r\n{\r\n    int *X;\r\n    int k;\r\n    float cota;\r\n};\r\nvoid quicksort(int *V, int izq, int der)\r\n{\r\n    int i, d, p;\r\n    int pivote;\r\n    int aux;\r\n    p=(izq+der)/2;\r\n    if(p>0)\r\n    {\r\n        pivote=V[p];\r\n        i=izq;\r\n        d=der;\r\n        while(i<=d)\r\n        {\r\n            while(V[i]<pivote)\r\n            {\r\n                i++;\r\n            }\r\n            while(V[d]>pivote)\r\n            {\r\n                d--;\r\n            }\r\n            if(i<=d)\r\n            {\r\n                aux=V[i];\r\n                V[i]=V[d];\r\n                V[d]=aux;\r\n                i++;\r\n                d--;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        if(izq<d)\r\n        {\r\n            quicksort(V, izq, d);\r\n        }\r\n        if(i<der)\r\n        {\r\n            quicksort(V, i, der);\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\nint tecnicos()\r\n{\r\n\tint tecnicos;\r\n\tcout<<"Introduzca el numero de tecnicos: "<<endl;\r\n\tcin>>tecnicos;\r\n\treturn tecnicos;\r\n}\r\nint sumatotal;\r\n    int cota;\r\n    int *veces;\r\n    sumatotal=0;\r\n    veces=new int[numTec+1];\r\n    for(i=1;i<=numTec;i++)\r\n    {\r\n        veces[i]=0;\r\n    }\r\n }\r\n    int *T;\r\n    for(i=1;i<=numTec;i++)\r\n    {\r\n        k=0;\r\n        T=new int[veces[i]+1];\r\n        for(j=1;j<=veces[i];j++)\r\n        {\r\n            T[i]=0;\r\n        }\r\n b'TIROIDA : LOCALIZARE : IN PARTEA ANTERIOARA A GATULUI INTR_O LOJA FIBROASA\r\nAlcatuire: doi lobi uniti printr-o portiune de tesut glandular numita istm\r\nHormoni secretati : tiroxina si triiodotironina\r\nTiroxina si triiodotironina: \r\nEfecte/actiuni : efect calorigen , manifestat prin cresterea metabolismului bazal, au rol in cresterea si dezvoltarea organismului, in special a sistemului nervos, stimuleaza catabolismul proteinelor si cresterea eliminarilor de N ,determina hoperglicemie(stimuleaza absortia intestinala a glucozei si oxidarea ei celulara) scar rezervele adipoase prin stimularea lipolizei, scad colesterolemia, produc iratibilitate, neliniste, stimuleaza activitatea gonadelor\r\nHipersecretie: la adult determina boala Basedow_ Graves ( gusa exoftalmica) cct. prin: scadere in greutate ,iratibiliatate, neliniste, hipertensiune, hiperfagie, gusa , ochi  exoftalmici , tahicardie , piele calda , si umeda.\r\nHiposecretie: la copil :nanismul tiroidian sau cretinismul sporadic cu gusa- cct prin: inaltime redusa, dezvoltare fizica, si pisihica redusa ( cretinism ) , defecte ale dintilor, deformari osoase etc.\r\nLA ADULT: mixedem cct prin crestere in greutate , senzatie permanenta de frig, edem mucos, piele uscata si ingrosata ,caderea parului , scaderea capacitatii de concentrare si invatare.\r\n--------------------------------\r\nSistemul endocrin este alcatuit din totalitatea glandelor endocrine ai caror produsi de secretie - hormonii- sunt eliberati in sange sau limfa\r\nrol: regleaza metabolismul celular\r\nprincipalele glande endocrine sunt: hipofiza, epifiza ,tiroida, paratiroidele ,timusul , pancreasul(glanda mixta), glandele suprarenale , gonadele(glande mixte).\r\nHIPOFIZA: localizare : la baza creierului , in saua turceasca a osului sfenoid\r\nalcatuire: 3 lobi: anterior, intermediar , posterior\r\nHIPOFIZA este legata de baza hipotalamusului prin tija pituitara formata din sistemul port-hipofizar si tractul hipotalamo-hipofizar\r\nLobul anterior hipofizar(adenohipofiza) - 75% din masa glandei\r\nHormoni secretati : a) hormoni glandulotropi: controleaza activitatea altor glande endocrine: titropina(TSH), corticotropina(ACTH), hormoni gonadotropi(h.luteinizant-LH si h.foliculostimulant-FSH)\r\nb) hormoni non-glandulotropi-h.somatotrop(STH) si prolactina\r\n------------\r\nPancreasul ENDOCRIN- Localizare in cavitatea abdominala, in spatele stomacului\r\nStructura: functia endocrina este asigurata de celulele insulelor Langerhans, care sunt de doua tipuri celule alfa(25%) secreta glucagon, celule beta(75%) secreta insulina\r\nINSULINA: Efecte/actiuni: produce hipoglicemie prin: stimularea patrunderii glucozei in tesutul  muscular si tesutul adipos; intensifica consumul de glucoza la nivel celular;stimuleaza glicogenogeneza hepatica(!!este principalul hormon hipoglicemiant al organismului)/stimuleaza lipogeneza(formarea de lipide) din glucoza, stimuleaza sinteza de proteine\r\nhipersecretie:determina hipoglicemie, scaderea fortei musculare, in stadii grave determina pierderea cunostintei si aparitia starii de coma\r\nhiposecretie: determina diabetul zaharat, caracterizat prin: hiperglicemie, poliurie, ploidipsie, polifage(Mananca mult), glucozurie(glucoza in urina), scadere in greutate, stare de apatie.\r\nGLUCAGON: produce hiperglicemie prin : stimularea glicogenolizei(descompunerea glicogenului in glucoza), stimularea gluconeogenezei(formarea de glucide din aminoacizi).\r\nGONADE: SUNT GLANDE MIXTE\r\nTESTICULE:localizate in regiunea inghinala\r\nstructura: contine tubi seminiferi care produc spermatozoizi si celule interstitiale Leydig care secreta hormonul sexual masculin=testosteron\r\nHormoni secretati: testosteron\r\nEfecte/Actiuni: stimuleaza cresterea si dezvoltarea organelor genitale masculine, asigura dezvoltarea si mentinerea caracterelor sexuale secundare, determina dezvoltarea masei musculare(anabolizant proteic)\r\nOVARE: localizate in regiunea pelviana\r\nstructura: contine o zona corticala, unde sunt prezenti foliculi ovarieni care secreta hormonii sexuali feminini si o zona medulara formata din sesut conjunctiv lax, vase de sange si nervi\r\nhormoni secretati:hormoni estrogeni: sunt sintetizati de: celulele foliculului ovarian, in timpul maturariii, corpul galben; placenta in timpul sarcinii;\r\nEfecte/Actiuni: stimuleaza proliferarea mucoasei si musculaturii uterine\r\n-stimuleaza dezvoltarea glandelor mamare\r\n-----------------------\r\nhormon : STH(de crestere) \r\nefecte /atiuni: stimuleaza cresterea oaselor lungi, stimuleaza dezvoltarea masei musculare, stimuleaza dezvoltarea organelor interne, stimuleaza sinteza de proteine, efect hiperglicemiant, determina mobilizarea acizilor grasi din depozitele lipidice, scade eliminarile de Na, K,Ca, P,N\r\nHipersecretie:la copii: determina gigantismul. la adult:det. acromegalia-cresterea extremitatilor si viscerelor\r\nHiposecretie: la copii: determina naismul hipofizar sau piticismul hipofizar-talie redusa, proportionat, dezvoltare psihica normala\r\nPROLACTINA:efecte/actiuni: la femeie stimuleaza dezvoltarea glandelor mamare si secretia lactata.\r\nTSH:REGLEAZA ACTIVITATEA SECRETORIE A TIROIDEI\r\nACTH: REGLeaza activitatea secretorie a corticosuprarenalelor.\r\nFSH: la femei det. cresterea si maturarea foliculilor ovarieni si secretia de estrogeni , la barbati stimuleaza spermatogeneza, la femei det. ovulatia si aparitia corpului galben, a carui secretie de progesteron si estrogeni o stimuleaza, la barbati stimuleaza secretia de testosteron\t\r\n\r\nLOBUL INTERMEDIAR HIPOFIZAR- 2% Din masa glandei\r\n-anatomic face parte din adenihipofiza \r\nHormoni secretati:h.  melanocitostimulator(MSH) -stimuleaza sinteza de melanina, in melanocita, cu rol in pigmetarea pielii\r\nLobul posterior hipofizar(neurohipofiza)\r\neste legat de hipotalamus prin tractul hipotalamo-hipofizar\r\nelibereaza 2 neurohormoni (ADH si ocitocina) care sunt secretati de nucleii hipotalamici anteriori.\r\nhormon: ADH:(h. antidiuretic/vasopresina) Efecte/a:stimuleaza absortia apei la nivelul nefronilor=> creste volemia, scade cantintatea de urina eliminata si creste concentratia urinara\r\nhipersecretie: scade diureza si creste concentratia urinara, creste tensiunea arteriala,de aceea,si denumirea de vasopresina\r\nhiposecretie:determina diabetul insipid:caracterizat prin:poliurie:(eliminarea unei mari cantitati de urina diluata), polidipsie(ingerarea unei mari cantitati de apa), hipotensiune\r\nocitocina/oxitocina: Stimuleaza contractia musculaturii uterului in timpul travaliului, ducand expulzia fatului. stimuleaza ejectia laptelui din glandele mamare\r\nProgesteronul(hormonul maternitatii): stimuleaza dezvoltarea caracterelor sexuale secundare la femei, actioneaza asupra mucoasei uterine, determinand modificari secretorii care o pregatesc pentru nidatie(fixarea celulei ou).\r\nsistemul digestiv este alcatuit din tub digestiv : (cavitate bucala, faringe, esofag, stomac, intestin subtire , intestin gros) \r\nglande anexe: salivare , ficat , pancreas\r\nDigestia= totalitatea transformarilor mecanice (taiere zdrobire triturare), fizice(umezirea alimentelor, dizolvarea subst, emulsierea grasimilor) si\r\n chimice(hidroliza enzimatica suferite de alimentele ingerate pana la transf subst org ecomplexe din acestea in substante org simple, solubile , nespecifice ,\r\nabsorbabile numite nutrimente.\r\nsb complexe alimentare -> transf mech,chimice,fizice - substante simple , solubile, nespecifice , absorbabile.\r\nproteine-> aminoacizi\r\nglucide-> monozaharide(glucoza, fructoza,galactoza)\r\nlipide->acizi grasi+glicerol 3. nutrimente\r\n\r\ndigestia bucala: in cavitatea bucala alimentele  sufera modificari mecanice, fizice si chimice\r\nare loc masticatia= proces prin care alimentele solide si semi solide sunt preluate mecanic prin taiere zdrobire si triturare , muschiilor masticatori prin \r\nparticiparea mandibulei , dintilor, buzelor , limbii si obrajilor.\r\nTransformari fizice: umezire, dizolvare ,cu ajutorul apei din saliva: este produsul glandelor salivare , compozitie chimica :\r\n 99.5% apa , 0.5 % rezid. uscat ( reprez. de subst anorganice ( cloruri, fosfati , bicarbonati de sodiu, pot.) si subst. organice: tialina (anilaza salivara)\r\nrolul salivei : inmuierea alimentelor, vorbire, protectie antibacteriala prin lozozim, form. bolului alim deglutitie.\r\nTransf. chimice : hidroliza enz. sub actiunea enzimei amilaza salivara(tialina)\r\nenzima salivara( amidon copt, preparat amil-> dextrine -> maltoza)\r\nDeglutitia=totalitatea proceselor prin care bolul alimentar format in cavitatea bucala strabate faringele esofagului ajungand in stomac , are loc in 3 timpi.\r\nbucal-voluntar , timpul faringean-involuntar , esofagian-involuntar.\r\n\r\nDigestia gastrica: la real. acestui proces colucreaza 2 functii ale stomacului: functia secretorie, motorie\r\nfunctia secretorie= consta in secretia de suc gastric produs de glandele gastrice. Comp. chimica a sucului gastric: apa : 99% , 1% rezid uscat repr de subst. \r\nanorganice ( acidul clorhidric cel mai imp). cloruri de rad., potasiu) si subst organice( enzime si mucus)\r\nRolul HCL: activeaza enzimele proteolitice din sucul gastric, stimuleaza evacuarea gastrica, are actiune anti septica(distruge germenii patogeni)\r\nRolul mucus:de autodistrugere sub act. pepsinei si de actiune coroziva a HCL\r\nEnzimele:part. la transf. chimice: 2 tipuri de enzime:proteolitice,ipolitice\r\nPROTELOLITICE: 1) pepsina:se secreta sub forma de proenzima inactiva num. pepsinogen\r\nFermentul: prezent la sugari det. coagularea transf. cast. solubil(din lapte) ->paracazeina->paracazeinat de Ca\r\n3)gelatinaza:lichefiaza gelatina\r\nLIPOLITICE: LIPAZA GASTRICA CARE HIDROLIZEAZA LIPIDE EMULSIANTE DIN LAPTE,FRISCA, LE TRANSFORMA in glicerol si acizi grasi si partial in mono gliceride.\r\nFunctia motorie:asigurata\tde musculatura neteda a stomacului prin 2 tipuri de miscari : misc tonice: de adaptare a capacit. stom. la continutul sau/ umplerea \r\nstomacului cu alimente\r\nmisc. peristaltice: unde de contractie si relaxare si care asigura amestecul alimentelor cu sucul gastric prin progresia continut. gastric spre'

b"create function fun_najplaceniji1()\r\nreturns table\r\nas\r\nreturn(\r\nselect *\r\nfrom radnik\r\nwhere plata = (select max(plata) from radnik))\r\n\r\ncreate function fun_brojRadnika\r\n( \r\n@kvalif nchar(30) \r\n) \r\nreturns int\r\nas\r\nbegin\r\ndeclare @broj_radnika int\r\nif NOT EXISTS (select kvalif from radnik where @kvalif = kvalif)\r\nbegin\r\nset @broj_radnika = 200\r\nend\r\nelse\r\nbegin\r\nselect @broj_radnika = count(Id_radnika)\r\nfrom radnik\r\nwhere  @kvalif = kvalif\r\nend\r\nreturn @broj_radnika\r\nend\r\n\r\ncreate trigger trig_Premija2\r\non Radnik\r\nafter update\r\nas\r\nif (update (premija))\r\nbegin\r\nselect 'Premija promenjena'\r\nend\r\n\r\ncreate view view_ORP1\r\nas\r\nselect ime_od, ime, ime_proj\r\nfrom odeljenje o inner join radnik r on o.Id_odeljenja = r.Id_odeljenja\r\ninner join ucesce u on u.Id_radnika = r.Id_radnika inner join projekat p on\r\np.Id_projekta = u.Id_projekta\r\nwhere year(sysdatetime()) - year(Dat_zap) > 20\r\n\r\ncreate procedure sp_Premesti1(@ime char(30), @prezime char(30), @ime_od char(30))\r\nas\r\nbegin\r\nif not exists (select id_radnika \r\n\t\t\t\tfrom radnik \r\n\t\t\t\twhere @ime = ime and prezime = @prezime and Id_odeljenja = (select Id_odeljenja from odeljenje where Ime_od = @ime))\r\nbegin\r\nupdate radnik\r\nset id_odeljenja=(select id_odeljenja from odeljenje where Ime_od=@ime_od)\r\nwhere ime=@ime and prezime=@prezime\r\nselect 'Radnik premesten'\r\nend\r\nelse\r\nbegin\r\nselect 'Radnik je vec u odeljenju'\r\nend\r\nend"

false;\r\nSlashed = false;\r\nGrabbing = false;\r\nGrabbed = false;\r\n}\r\nlocal Touche = {char.Name, }\r\n----------------------------------------------------\r\nfunction lerp(a, b, t) -- Linear interpolation\r\n    return a + (b - a)*t\r\nend\r\n \r\nfunction slerp(a, b, t) --Spherical interpolation\r\n    dot = a:Dot(b)\r\n    if dot > 0.99999 or dot < -0.99999 then\r\n        return t <= 0.5 and a or b\r\n    else\r\n        r = math.acos(dot)\r\n        return (a*math.sin((1 - t)*r) + b*math.sin(t*r)) / math.sin(r)\r\n    end\r\nend\r\n \r\nfunction matrixInterpolate(a, b, t)\r\n    local ax, ay, az, a00, a01, a02, a10, a11, a12, a20, a21, a22 = a:components()\r\n    local bx, by, bz, b00, b01, b02, b10, b11, b12, b20, b21, b22 = b:components()\r\n    local v0 = lerp(Vector3.new(ax, ay, az), Vector3.new(bx , by , bz), t) -- Position\r\n    local v1 = slerp(Vector3.new(a00, a01, a02), Vector3.new(b00, b01, b02), t) -- Vector  right\r\n    local v2 = slerp(Vector3.new(a10, a11, a12), Vector3.new(b10, b11, b12), t) -- Vector  up\r\n    local v3 = slerp(Vector3.new(a20, a21, a22), Vector3.new(b20, b21, b22), t) -- Vector  back\r\n    local t = v1:Dot(v2)\r\n    if not (t < 0 or t == 0 or t > 0) then     -- Failsafe\r\n        return CFrame.new()\r\n    end\r\n    return CFrame.new(\r\n    v0.x, v0.y, v0.z,\r\n    v1.x, v1.y, v1.z,\r\n    v2.x, v2.y, v2.z,\r\n    v3.x, v3.y, v3.z)\r\nend\r\n----------------------------------------------------\r\nfunction genWeld(a,b)\r\n    local w = Instance.new("Weld",a)\r\n    w.Part0 = a\r\n    w.Part1 = b\r\n    return w\r\nend\r\nfunction weld(a, b)\r\n    local weld = Instance.new("Weld")\r\n    weld.Name = "W"\r\n    weld.Part0 = a\r\n    weld.Part1 = b\r\n    weld.C0 = a.CFrame:inverse() * b.CFrame\r\n    weld.Parent = a\r\n    return weld;\r\nend\r\n----------------------------------------------------\r\nfunction Lerp(c1,c2,al)\r\nlocal com1 = {c1.X,c1.Y,c1.Z,c1:toEulerAnglesXYZ()}\r\nlocal com2 = {c2.X,c2.Y,c2.Z,c2:toEulerAnglesXYZ()}\r\nfor i,v in pairs(com1) do \r\ncom1[i] = v+(com2[i]-v)*al\r\nend\r\nreturn CFrame.new(com1[1],com1[2],com1[3]) * CFrame.Angles(select(4,unpack(com1)))\r\nend\r\n----------------------------------------------------\r\nnewWeld = function(wp0, wp1, wc0x, wc0y, wc0z)\r\nlocal wld = Instance.new("Weld", wp1)\r\nwld.Part0 = wp0\r\nwld.Part1 = wp1\r\nwld.C0 = CFrame.new(wc0x, wc0y, wc0z)\r\nend\r\n----------------------------------------------------\r\nfor i,v in math.acos\r\n\t\tlocal sqrt = math.sqrt\r\n\t\tlocal Vec3 = Vector3.new\r\n\t\tlocal fromAxisAngle = CFrame.fromAxisAngle\r\n\r\n\t\tlocal function toAxisAngle(CFr)\r\n\t\t\tlocal X,Y,Z,R00,R01,R02,R10,R11,R12,R20,R21,R22 = CFr:components()\r\n\t\t\tlocal Angle = math.acos((R00+R11+R22-1)/2)\r\n\t\t\tlocal A = (R21-R12)^2+(R02-R20)^2+(R10-R01)^2\r\n\t\t\tA = A == 0 and 0.00001 or A\r\n\t\t\tlocal B = (R21-R12)^2+(R02-R20)^2+(R10-R01)^2\r\n\t\t\tB = B == 0 and 0.00001 or B\r\n\t\t\tlocal C = (R21-R12)^2+(R02-R20)^2+(R10-R01)^2\r\n\t\t\tC = C == 0 and 0.00001 or C\r\n\t\t\tlocal x = (R21-R12)/sqrt(A)\r\n\t\t\tlocal y = (R02-R20)/sqrt(B)\r\n\t\t\tlocal z = (R10-R01)/sqrt(C)\r\n\t\t\treturn Vec3(x,y,z),Angle\r\n\t\tend\r\n\r\n\t\tfunction ApplyTrig(Num,Func)\r\n\t\t\tlocal Min,Max = Func(0),Func(1)\r\n\t\t\tlocal i = Func(Num)\r\n\t\t\treturn (i-Min)/(Max-Min)\r\n\t\tend\r\n\r\n\t\tfunction LerpCFrame(CFrame1,CFrame2,Num)\r\n\t\t\tlocal Vec,Ang = toAxisAngle(CFrame1:inverse()*CFrame2)\r\n\t\t\treturn CFrame1*fromAxisAngle(Vec,Ang*Num) + (CFrame2.p-CFrame1.p)*Num\r\n\t\tend\r\n\r\n\t\tfunction Crater(Torso,Radius)\r\n\t\t\tSpawn(function()\r\n\t\t\t\tlocal Ray = Ray.new(Torso.Position,Vector3.new(0,-1,0)*10)\r\n\t\t\t\tlocal Ignore = newRay(start,face,range,wat)\r\n        local rey=Ray.new(start.p,(face.p-start.p).Unit*range)\r\n        hit,pos=Workspace:FindPartOnRayWithIgnoreList(rey,wat)\r\n        return rey,hit,pos\r\nend\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nfat = Instance.new("BindableEvent",script)\r\nfat.Name = "Heartbeat"\r\n\r\nscript:WaitForChild("Heartbeat")\r\n\r\nframe = 1/30\r\ntf = 0\r\nallowframeloss = false --if set to true will fire every frame it possibly can. This will result in multiple events happening at the same time whenever delta returns frame*2 or greater.\r\ntossremainder = false --if set to true t will be set to 0 after Fire()-ing.\r\nlastframe = tick()\r\nscript.Heartbeat:Fire() --ayy lmao\r\n\r\ngame:GetService("RunService").Heartbeat:connect(function(s,p) --herp derp\r\n\ttf = tf + s\r\n\tif tf >= frame then\r\n\t\tif allowframeloss then\r\n\t\t\tscript.Heartbeat:Fire()\r\n\t\t\tlastframe=tick()\r\n\t\telse\r\n\t\t\t--print("FIRED "..math.floor(t/frame).." FRAME(S)","REMAINDER "..(t - frame*(math.floor(t/frame))))\r\n\t\t\tfor i=1, math.floor(tf/frame) do\r\n\t\t\t\tscript.Heartbeat:Fire()\r\n\t\t\tend\r\n\t\t\tlastframe=tick()\r\n\t\tend\r\n\t\tif tossremainder then\r\n\t\t\ttf = 0\r\n\t\telse\r\n\t\t\ttf = tf - frame * math.floor(tf/frame)\r\n\t\tend\r\n\tend\r\nend)\r\n\r\nfunction Swait(NUMBER)\r\n\tif NUMBER == 0 or NUMBER == nil then\r\n\t\tfat.Event:wait()\r\n\telse\r\n\t\tfor i = 1, NUMBER do\r\n\t\t\tfat.Event:wait()\r\n\t\tend\r\n\tend\r\nend\r\n\r\nfunction Landing2()\r\n\tlocal rng = Instance.new("Part", char)\r\n
